## ⚙️ Deployment Workflow

```
Code Push →
   Build →
      Package →
         Deploy to Staging →
            Slot Swap →
               Production (Zero Downtime)
```

---

## 🚀 Azure CLI Setup

### 1️⃣ Create Resource Group
```bash
az group create --name elearning-rg --location westus3
```

### 2️⃣ Create App Service Plan (B1 Required)
```bash
az appservice plan create \
  --name elearning-plan \
  --resource-group elearning-rg \
  --sku B1 \
  --is-linux
```

### 3️⃣ Create Web App (PHP)
```bash
az webapp create \
  --resource-group elearning-rg \
  --plan elearning-plan \
  --name elearning-app-12345 \
  --runtime "PHP|8.2"
```

### 4️⃣ Create Staging Slot
```bash
az webapp deployment slot create \
  --name elearning-app-12345 \
  --resource-group elearning-rg \
  --slot staging
```

---

## 🌐 Azure DNS Configuration

### Create DNS Zone
```bash
az network dns zone create \
  --resource-group elearning-rg \
  --name auemeribetech.com.ng
```

### Add CNAME Record
```bash
az network dns record-set cname set-record \
  --resource-group elearning-rg \
  --zone-name auemeribetech.com.ng \
  --record-set-name www \
  --cname elearning-app-12345.azurewebsites.net
```

### Add TXT Record
```bash
az network dns record-set txt add-record \
  --resource-group elearning-rg \
  --zone-name auemeribetech.com.ng \
  --record-set-name asuid.www \
  --value "<verification-id>"
```

### Bind Custom Domain
```bash
az webapp config hostname add \
  --webapp-name elearning-app-12345 \
  --resource-group elearning-rg \
  --hostname www.auemeribetech.com.ng
```

---

## 🔐 GitHub Secrets

```bash
gh secret set AZURE_WEBAPP_NAME --body "elearning-app-12345"
gh secret set AZURE_WEBAPP_PUBLISH_PROFILE_PROD < prod-profile.xml
gh secret set AZURE_WEBAPP_PUBLISH_PROFILE_STAGING < staging-profile.xml
gh secret set AZURE_CREDENTIALS
```

---

## ⚙️ CI/CD Workflow (Enterprise Pipeline)

📁 Location: `.github/workflows/deploy.yml`

### 🔧 Workflow Stages:
- 🏗️ Build & Package
- 🚀 Deploy to Staging
- 🔁 Swap to Production (Zero Downtime)

```yaml
name: Enterprise CI/CD - PHP App

on:
  push:
    branches:
      - main

jobs:

  build:
    name: 🏗️ Build & Package Application
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest

    steps:
    - name: 📥 Checkout Source Code
      uses: actions/checkout@v3

    - name: 📦 Package Application
      run: zip -r app.zip .

    - name: ⬆️ Upload Build Artifact
      uses: actions/upload-artifact@v3
      with:
        name: php-app
        path: app.zip

  deploy-staging:
    name: 🚀 Deploy to Staging Slot
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    needs: build

    steps:
    - name: 📥 Download Artifact
      uses: actions/download-artifact@v3
      with:
        name: php-app

    - name: 🚀 Deploy to Azure (Staging)
      uses: azure/webapps-deploy@v2
      with:
        app-name: ${{ secrets.AZURE_WEBAPP_NAME }}
        slot-name: staging
        publish-profile: ${{ secrets.AZURE_WEBAPP_PUBLISH_PROFILE_STAGING }}
        package: app.zip

  swap-to-production:
    name: 🔁 Swap Staging → Production
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    needs: deploy-staging

    steps:
    - name: 🔐 Azure Login
      uses: azure/login@v1
      with:
        creds: ${{ secrets.AZURE_CREDENTIALS }}

    - name: 🔁 Perform Slot Swap
      run: |
        az webapp deployment slot swap \
          --name ${{ secrets.AZURE_WEBAPP_NAME }} \
          --resource-group elearning-rg \
          --slot staging \
          --target-slot production
```

