## ❌ Common Issues & Fixes

| Issue | Solution |
|------|--------|
| Domain not resolving | Check CNAME & wait |
| Cannot add domain | Upgrade to B1 |
| HTTPS not working | Bind SSL |
| CI/CD not triggering | Check GitHub Actions |

